metadata.name: Dryads Call
metadata.description:
Behold the mother tree in her lucid splendour and surrender yourself to her tightly knotted roots.

For she will show your spirits calling and lead you to the truth.

Dryads Call is the first piece in my new collection "Artifacts Incarnate" Wherein i explore the dance between the machine and the guided hand making collages of AI elements and bridging them with hand painted scenery.

Be sure to follow my progress on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/WitherBloomArt).

1664 X  1664
2.24mb
Created using text to art - GIMP 2.10 - Corel Painter

WitherBloom - 9/08/2022
